fetch(targetUrl)
    .then((response) => response.text())
    .then((mdText) => {
        //...原来的代码
    });
这样一来，你就可以避免 CORS 错误，因为 Netlify 默认允许所有跨域请求。注意：请将 your-site-name 替换为你实际的 Netlify 站点名称。

In this answer, I will provide you with a simple REST API using Node.js and Express.js for a Todo List application, as well as another API for basic arithmetic operations. For the purpose of this example, I'll use an in-memory array to store the todo items. In a real-world application, you would use a database.First, create a new directory for your project and initialize it with npm:bashCopy codemkdir todo-api
cd todo-api
